cs.CL, cs.AI, cs.LG, cs.NE, cs.CV 

This paper is likely to belong to the arXiv CS sub-category cs.CL (Computation and Language) as it deals with machine translation using neural encoder-decoder framework. Additionally, it may also belong to cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence) and cs.LG (Machine Learning) as it involves training a model to maximize the probability of a target string. It may also belong to cs.NE (Neural and Evolutionary Computing) as it uses a neural network for translation. Finally, it may belong to cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition) as it involves exploring combination methods for improving translation quality.
